00:19:20,359 --> 00:19:21,792
Ili oba?

236
00:19:22,427 --> 00:19:24,122
Ili oba.

237
00:19:27,699 --> 00:19:31,692
Pa..vreme je za lekove
mog muza.

238
00:19:32,804 --> 00:19:34,738
Moram da ga nahranim.

239
00:19:34,907 --> 00:19:37,808
Nadam se da cete lepo spavati.
- Da.

240
00:19:38,744 --> 00:19:40,371
Laku noc.

241
00:19:44,816 --> 00:19:47,808
'Nakon sto sam upoznao  Meeru...
shvatio sam jednu stvar.'

242
00:19:48,453 --> 00:19:52,583
'Ona je bila mnogo vise
nepotpuna od mene.'

243
00:19:53,125 --> 00:19:57,687
''Bilo joj lakse od mene.''

244
00:19:58,597 --> 00:20:04,661
'Ona je opterecena mnogo vise
tajni od mene.''

245
00:20:05,671 --> 00:20:09,163
'I negde ...
izmedju njenih tajni i mojih...'

246
00:20:09,541 --> 00:20:11,600
'...je pocela moja prica.'

247
00:20:13,579 --> 00:20:16,343
'Od te noci...
prica je pocela novim zaokretom.'

248
00:23:53,432 --> 00:23:55,992
Budi se!

249
00:24:20,025 --> 00:24:29,127
''Moj voljeni ce se vratiti.''

250
00:24:29,234 --> 00:24:35,366
''Vratice se.''

251
00:24:44,049 --> 00:24:51,854
''Kao sto su lampe bez
plamena?''

252
00:24:52,190 --> 00:24:59,619
''Kao lampe sto su bez
plamena.''

253
00:25:00,532 --> 00:25:08,371
''Kao sto je strelac,
bez strele.''

254
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:11,068
''Neko ce planuti.''

255
00:26:55,513 --> 00:26:57,378
Da li si u redu?

256
00:26:58,316 --> 00:27:01,285
Neko..neko je ovde.

257
00:27:01,786 --> 00:27:03,947
Video sam njegov odraz.

258
00:27:04,222 --> 00:27:06,747
Radio..to je bilo.

259
00:27:06,825 --> 00:27:10,226
Vatra se upalila.

260
00:27:11,296 --> 00:27:14,788
There was a fire burning here.
I saw it with my own eyes and..

261
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,664
Ne!

262
00:27:16,901 --> 00:27:18,960
Slika...

263
00:27:19,237 --> 00:27:20,397
Slika...

264
00:27:20,472 --> 00:27:23,100
Covek sa slike je sedeo
ovde.

265
00:27:23,575 --> 00:27:24,473
Ja...

266
00:27:24,576 --> 00:27:25,770
Knjiga.

267
00:27:25,844 --> 00:27:27,311
Ovo...

268
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:30,747
Pogledaj...

269
00:27:31,249 --> 00:27:34,741
..ponekad kada vetar duva
u dolini...

270
00:27:34,919 --> 00:27:38,753
...skripi drvo jer je kuca stara,
i izgleda kao da se cuju koraci...

271
00:27:39,157 --> 00:27:43,617
Dugo si putovao,
sigurno si i umoran.

272
00:27:44,262 --> 00:27:47,026
Ja mislim da se trebas naspavati.

273
00:27:48,933 --> 00:27:50,298
Da!

274
00:28:33,211 --> 00:28:35,475
Zovem vas vec tri dana..

275
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:38,114
..dao sam vam garanciju..

276
00:28:38,349 --> 00:28:40,613
..ali mog paketa jos nema.

277
00:28:41,386 --> 00:28:42,512
Da.

278
00:28:43,121 --> 00:28:45,021
Koliko jos puta treba da vam dam
moju adresu?

279
00:28:45,156 --> 00:28:46,521
Dobro,zapisite.

280
00:28:47,459 --> 00:28:50,758
5, Lakeside Manor.
Hussain Road, Manasar.

281
00:28:50,962 --> 00:28:52,623
19001.

282
00:28:52,797 --> 00:28:53,923
I da..

283
00:28:54,032 --> 00:28:56,660
Ako ja ne budem kuci,
moja zena  ce biti.

284
00:28:56,768 --> 00:28:58,463
Mozete dati paket njoj.

285
00:29:09,948 --> 00:29:11,643
Ponekad je potrebno da potsetim ljude...

286
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,877
...da ima muskarca u ovoj kuci.

287
00:29:14,285 --> 00:29:15,616
U suprotnom..duga je
lista ljudi...

288
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,654
...koji vole same zene.

289
00:29:17,889 --> 00:29:19,049
Da.

290
00:29:21,159 --> 00:29:25,619
Dakle..gde planiras da ides sa torbom?

291
00:29:26,131 --> 00:29:30,397
Nigde.Razmisljao sam
da napravim neku razglednicu.

292
00:29:30,802 --> 00:29:32,667
I malo da se inspirisem.

293
00:29:34,506 --> 00:29:37,805
Ili mozda..ides da
potrazis pricu

294
00:29:38,143 --> 00:29:40,134
Tako nekako.

295
00:29:40,912 --> 00:29:42,812
Napravila sam ti dorucak.

296
00:29:42,947 --> 00:29:46,314
Ili zelite da pobegnete napolje
bez jela.

297
00:29:46,417 --> 00:29:48,408
Ne,doruckovacu u nekom
kaficu...

298
00:29:48,486 --> 00:29:50,920
Ne treba reci ne hrani.

299
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:53,348
Spakovacu vam.

300
00:29:53,591 --> 00:29:55,616
U redu je,zaista.
- Dajte mi samo dva minuta.

301
00:29:55,693 --> 00:29:57,285
U redu je.

302
00:30:00,498 --> 00:30:03,934
Dakle,sta ti predlazes?

303
00:30:04,836 --> 00:30:06,326
Sta vredi posetiti ovde?

304
00:30:06,437 --> 00:30:09,964
Imate Shivin hram
nedaleko odavde.

305
00:30:10,141 --> 00:30:12,803
Ima i vrtovi,
ali oni su malo stari.

306
00:30:12,877 --> 00:30:16,040
Ima i jezero.
Ljudi idu na plovidbu tamo ponekad.

307
00:30:16,181 --> 00:30:17,944
Kako da dodjem do Shivinog hrama?

308
00:30:18,049 --> 00:30:25,114
Malo napred odavde ima prodavnica
na raskrsnici.

309
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:29,487
Skrenite levo,i idite samo napred.

310
00:30:30,295 --> 00:30:31,660
Hvala vam.

311
00:30:32,497 --> 00:30:34,829
- Ne bih trebalo reci ne hrani.

312
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:38,030
- To sam cuo posle
mnogo vremena.

313
00:30:38,303 --> 00:30:42,330
- Posle duzeg vremena osecam
kao da je nekome stalo do mog obroka.

314
00:30:43,074 --> 00:30:45,736
- Neciji mali gestovi,
su poceli dodirivati moje srce.

315
00:30:46,244 --> 00:30:49,236
- Ali neke stvari koje je
cinila Meera cinile su me srecnim...

316
00:30:49,347 --> 00:30:51,975
- ...ali neke stvari su me
mnogo zbunjivale.

317
00:30:52,050 --> 00:30:53,813
Izvini te,gospodine.

318
00:30:53,918 --> 00:30:55,510
Da,gospodine.

319
00:30:55,887 --> 00:30:59,220
Ima li prodavnice ovde.

320
00:30:59,290 --> 00:31:00,951
Rekli su mi da ima ovde jedna.

321
00:31:01,659 --> 00:31:03,490
Da gospodine,ali se
zatvorila prosle godine.

322
00:31:03,595 --> 00:31:05,620
Sada se preselila u gradu.

323
00:31:24,515 --> 00:31:27,780
Zatvorili su prodavnicu prosle godine.

324
00:31:35,994 --> 00:31:38,690
Niste izlazili iz kuce odavno.

325
00:31:40,465 --> 00:31:41,898
Da li sam u pravu?

326
00:31:42,967 --> 00:31:44,867
Izvini te.

327
00:31:48,573 --> 00:31:50,507
Izvini te,mislio sam...

328
00:31:50,975 --> 00:31:53,409
...da od prosle godine to niste
primetili ...

329
00:31:53,578 --> 00:31:56,376
...a ta raskrsnica je samo
na kilometar od vase kuce.

330
00:31:56,714 --> 00:31:58,375
U pravu sam,ili gresim?

331
00:32:00,618 --> 00:32:04,611
Tvoju pricu trazis u ovoj
kuci.

332
00:32:04,756 --> 00:32:06,451
Ne drugde.

333
00:32:06,624 --> 00:32:09,354
Ona te je i dovela ovde.

334
00:32:10,662 --> 00:32:12,857
U pravu sam,ili gresim?

335
00:32:16,534 --> 00:32:18,832
Ti svaki razgovor napravis
komplikovan.

336
00:32:20,972 --> 00:32:23,964
Ako su stvari lake,
kako cete onda pronaci svoju pricu?

337
00:32:24,309 --> 00:32:26,800
Ako imam pravo,
postavicu vam jedno pitanje.

338
00:32:27,545 --> 00:32:29,638
Koju tajnu krijete?

339
00:32:29,814 --> 00:32:35,013
Da bi saznao moju tajnu..
moras biti veoma iskren.

340
00:32:37,221 --> 00:32:38,950
Tacno je.

341
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:41,717
Ja vidim pricu ovde.

342
00:32:42,393 --> 00:32:44,224
Eto sada znas.

343
00:32:46,030 --> 00:32:48,055
Hajde da uradimo
ovako..

344
00:32:49,534 --> 00:32:51,900
..zaboravite moju pricu.

345
00:32:53,071 --> 00:32:55,335
Zasto ne napises pricu...

346
00:32:55,406 --> 00:32:59,399
..koja se polako
razvija ovde?

347
00:33:01,112 --> 00:33:02,409
Kako to mislite?

348
00:33:06,317 --> 00:33:08,649
O usamljenoj kuci..

349
00:33:09,587 --> 00:33:12,181
...I same devojke...

350
00:33:12,957 --> 00:33:15,152
..ciji je muz bolestan..

351
00:33:16,627 --> 00:33:19,653
Putnik odjednom stigne..

352
00:33:21,933 --> 00:33:23,867
I uskoro sazna..

353
00:33:23,935 --> 00:33:27,701
..da postoji skrivena tajna
u ovoj kuci..

354
00:33:29,073 --> 00:33:32,509
..on zeli da se priblizi devojki..

355
00:33:33,578 --> 00:33:36,103
..ali okleva.

356
00:33:37,215 --> 00:33:41,174
A devojka..ona zna...

357
00:33:42,587 --> 00:33:46,853
..da postoji jedan covek koji moze...

358
00:33:47,258 --> 00:33:51,217
..razbiti zidove oko sebe..

359
00:33:53,498 --> 00:33:56,194
...to je on.

360
00:33:57,969 --> 00:34:00,836
Cudna dilema.

361
00:34:03,808 --> 00:34:05,275
I onda...

362
00:34:16,287 --> 00:34:21,691
''Sada znam misli,
tvoga srca.''

363
00:34:21,759 --> 00:34:26,890
''Tisinu koju si
skrivala od sveta.''

364
00:34:27,365 --> 00:34:32,530
''Sada sam barem upoznat
sa tvojim mislima.''

365
00:34:32,637 --> 00:34:38,132
''Sta skrivas
u sebi.''

366
00:34:38,242 --> 00:34:45,239
''Iz tvojih ociju sam
citao tvoje misli..''

367
00:34:45,349 --> 00:34:52,448
''Negde sam montiram
u tvom srcu da kuca.''

368
00:34:52,557 --> 00:35:05,402
''Svakog trenutka si uz mene.''

369
00:35:05,937 --> 00:35:15,539
''Da li sam ti blizu ili daleko..''

370
00:35:48,379 --> 00:36:01,918
''Tuzni ste svakoga dana
vidim to..''

371
00:36:02,026 --> 00:36:08,226
''Veoma ste tihi.''

372
00:36:08,299 --> 00:36:15,205
''Kada ne kazem,
ono sto cujem o vama.''

373
00:36:15,306 --> 00:36:21,802
''Dala si mi razloga da zivim.''

374
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:31,521
''Ne skrivaj to u sebi..''

375
00:36:31,956 --> 00:36:44,767
''Svaki trenutak si vezana za mene.''

376
00:36:45,369 --> 00:36:58,510
''Da li sam bio blizu,ili daleko..''

377
00:37:20,938 --> 00:37:27,070
''Neke stvari ti zelim reci
na tvojim usnama.''

378
00:37:27,411 --> 00:37:33,941
''Da li samo ja zivim u tvome srcu.''

379
00:37:34,552 --> 00:37:40,957
''Tvoj dah kaze da.''

380
00:37:41,025 --> 00:37:47,692
''Kada te dodirnem,ili drzim za ruku.''

381
00:37:48,065 --> 00:37:54,300
''Reci mi sta zelis..''

382
00:37:54,739 --> 00:38:03,477
''..ovo je vreme,
sve priznati.''

383
00:38:04,415 --> 00:38:17,488
''Svakog trenutka si uz mene.''

384
00:38:17,895 --> 00:38:31,070
''Da li sam blizu,ili daleko..''

385
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,807
Meera!
- Zao mi je, Kabir.

386
00:38:37,882 --> 00:38:39,349
Molim te,odlazi.

387
00:38:39,417 --> 00:38:41,408
Ponekad si mi tako blizu,
a ponekad tako daleko.

388
00:38:41,519 --> 00:38:43,453
Zasto? Zasto?
Sta je ovo?

389
00:38:43,554 --> 00:38:46,022
Kabir, molim te pusti me.
- Ne, ne...

390
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:47,748
Znam da mi nista neces
reci.

391
00:38:47,858 --> 00:38:48,916
Ali barem mi reci...

392
00:38:49,026 --> 00:38:51,654
...zelis li biti blizu mene
i ako je situacija drugacija?

393
00:38:51,729 --> 00:38:53,924
Situacija nije drugacija, Kabir.
- Sta ako jeste?

394
00:38:54,031 --> 00:38:55,692
Ali nije.

395
00:38:55,766 --> 00:38:57,393
Ali moze biti.

396
00:38:57,535 --> 00:38:58,832
Molim te.

397
00:38:59,036 --> 00:38:59,832
Nasta ti mislis?

398
00:38:59,904 --> 00:39:01,895
Postoji jedno mesto gde se
ispunjavaju zelje.

399
00:39:02,006 --> 00:39:02,995
Podji samnom.

400
00:39:03,074 --> 00:39:04,473
Kabir, ovo je ludo?
Sta to radis?

401
00:39:04,542 --> 00:39:06,373
I ja zelim da znam
da li je ovo ludilo.

402
00:39:06,477 --> 00:39:09,503
Ne mogu napustiti ovu kucu,ok.
- Zasto?

403
00:39:09,613 --> 00:39:11,513
Zasto?
Zasto ne mozes?

404
00:39:11,949 --> 00:39:13,416
Ne mogu,
to je to.

405
00:39:13,517 --> 00:39:15,678
Zasto? Ok...dobro...dobro.

406
00:39:15,786 --> 00:39:19,187
Samo mi reci..da li zelis biti blizu mene
ili ne.

407
00:39:19,290 --> 00:39:21,815
To nije tako jednostavno.
- Da li zelis ili ne?

408
00:39:21,892 --> 00:39:23,416
Kabir.
- Da,ili ne.

409
00:39:23,527 --> 00:39:26,018
Da,ali...
- To je to..podji samnom..

410
00:39:28,366 --> 00:39:29,196
Kabir.

411
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:30,699
Kabir, saslusaj me.

412
00:39:31,869 --> 00:39:33,302
Pravimo veliku gresku.

413
00:39:33,371 --> 00:39:34,702
Ne radimo nista lose.

414
00:39:34,872 --> 00:39:36,567
Ovo je prava stvar.

415
00:39:36,907 --> 00:39:38,204
Prokletstvo.

416
00:39:48,919 --> 00:39:51,353
Pandey, napisi izvestaj.
- Da,gospodine.

417
00:39:51,422 --> 00:39:53,515
To je bio nesrecan slucaj.
- Ok,gospodine.

418
00:39:56,527 --> 00:39:58,722
Pogledaj te gospodine,
ovo je nesrecni slucaj.

419
00:39:58,863 --> 00:40:00,125
Zato cemo morati uzeti izvestaj.

420
00:40:00,231 --> 00:40:02,062
Sada,ili u policiskoj stanici.

421
00:40:02,199 --> 00:40:03,564
Moze sada.

422
00:40:04,902 --> 00:40:06,199
Sta se dogodilo?

423
00:40:07,638 --> 00:40:10,129
Vozili smo na dole
prema jezeru,i odjednom..

424
00:40:10,241 --> 00:40:12,937
Kamion je odjenom isao pravo na nas..

425
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:15,374
..uspeli smo da ga izbegnemo u zadnjem minutu..

426
00:40:15,446 --> 00:40:17,243
..dok smo izbegli..

427
00:40:17,348 --> 00:40:19,407
...udarili smo kola u drvo.

428
00:40:19,483 --> 00:40:21,348
Desava se to.

429
00:40:21,786 --> 00:40:23,981
Kamiondzije ne paze...

430
00:40:24,221 --> 00:40:26,485
...prosli vikend je jedan ostao bez gume.

431
00:40:26,657 --> 00:40:28,591
To se desilo prosle nedelje.

432
00:40:42,873 --> 00:40:44,135
Hvala vam.

433
00:40:46,777 --> 00:40:48,768
Zasto si dala laznu izjavu.

434
00:40:48,879 --> 00:40:50,972
Zar nisi videla coveka
na putu?

435
00:40:51,081 --> 00:40:52,514
Rekla sam ti...

436
00:40:52,616 --> 00:40:54,584
...da ne mogu napustiti ovu kucu.

437
00:40:54,652 --> 00:40:56,483
Ali me nisi slusao.

438
00:40:56,587 --> 00:41:00,079
Mislis sve ovo je moja krivica.
- Laku noc, Kabir.

439
00:41:18,075 --> 00:41:19,474
Gde si bila?

440
00:41:19,577 --> 00:41:21,204
Cekao sam te dva sata.

441
00:41:21,278 --> 00:41:23,075
Zao mi je,
zao mi je.

442
00:41:23,147 --> 00:41:24,739
Ja...
- Gde je auto?

443
00:41:25,149 --> 00:41:26,776
Pogledao sam kroz prozor
i auto nije bio tu.

444
00:41:27,084 --> 00:41:30,349
Ne radi lepo,
parkirala sam ga u garazu..

445
00:41:30,421 --> 00:41:31,217
...pa sam ga sklonila.

446
00:41:31,322 --> 00:41:32,846
Nema nikoga
da mi da lekove...

447
00:41:32,923 --> 00:41:34,447
...ni da me nahrani.

448
00:41:34,558 --> 00:41:36,389
Dosta mi je ovog zivota.

449
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:37,927
Moram da zavisim
od svih vas.

450
00:41:37,995 --> 00:41:41,089
Jaidev, rekla sam ti izvini.
- Sta izvini.

451
00:41:41,165 --> 00:41:43,725
Donecu ti hranu odmah.

452
00:42:08,192 --> 00:42:10,820
'Te noci...
bio sam van sebe...'

453
00:42:10,928 --> 00:42:13,192
'...zbog Meere i
njenih lazi...'

454
00:42:13,464 --> 00:42:15,455
'...da nisam cuo
stvarnost...'

455
00:42:15,533 --> 00:42:18,161
'...vristao bih od ljutnje.'

456
00:42:18,802 --> 00:42:22,431
'Ostavio sam vezu ponovo
nekompletnom.'

457
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:28,940
'Kada je moj um konacno
shvatio...'

458
00:42:30,214 --> 00:42:34,583
...bio sam bespomocan na
Meerine lazi.

459
00:42:34,985 --> 00:42:41,083
'A bespomocna je i ona
jer ne moze vise da izdrzi.'

460
00:42:42,293 --> 00:42:45,057
'A ublazavanje bola...'

461
00:42:45,462 --> 00:42:48,124
'...bilo je neophodno za mene.'

462
00:42:53,137 --> 00:42:54,104
Zdravo.

463
00:42:55,639 --> 00:42:56,765
Da li je neko tu?

464
00:43:00,511 --> 00:43:01,671
Zdravo.

465
00:43:02,212 --> 00:43:04,112
Kao sto sam i rekao...

466
00:43:05,416 --> 00:43:07,247
..vratices se.

467
00:43:07,351 --> 00:43:09,911
Posto ste znali,
sigurno znate i ostatak.

468
