01:08:34,810 --> 01:08:38,678
Sto znaci da niste imali priliku
da ga napunite.

706
01:08:39,682 --> 01:08:42,480
To znaci da ste daleko od kuce
vec cele noci.

707
01:08:42,651 --> 01:08:45,484
Mokro zemljiste na vasim farmerkama
se vec osusilo.

708
01:08:46,555 --> 01:08:49,786
Sto znaci da ste bili praceni kisom
u nekom podrucju.

709
01:08:50,192 --> 01:08:53,025
A tri dana u ovoj oblasti nije padala kisa.

710
01:08:53,095 --> 01:08:57,794
Sto znaci da vas je oluja
pratila od Jammula.

711
01:08:59,802 --> 01:09:03,670
Prljave pantalone i prazan telefon..

712
01:09:05,975 --> 01:09:08,569
..ides iz grada ali nisi uspela da uzmes nikakav novac...

713
01:09:08,644 --> 01:09:10,509
...zbog toga nisi
uspela da krenes vozom...

714
01:09:10,613 --> 01:09:13,309
...nema nikakve kabine,ni luksuznog
autobusa...

715
01:09:14,583 --> 01:09:16,915
Tetovaza na tvojoj ruci pise MJ.

716
01:09:18,454 --> 01:09:23,858
I ne vidim kako slovo 'M' i
'J' moze se citati kao Priya.

717
01:09:28,564 --> 01:09:32,660
Devojka iz grada bez torbi
i prtljaga.

718
01:09:34,036 --> 01:09:36,129
I laze.

719
01:09:36,505 --> 01:09:38,166
Ali zasto?

720
01:09:38,707 --> 01:09:41,608
Zato sto bezi od nekoga.

721
01:09:42,711 --> 01:09:44,303
Zar ne?

722
01:09:48,017 --> 01:09:50,008
Sta ti se desilo.

723
01:09:50,853 --> 01:09:54,789
Ne mozete brinuti o sebi,
u ovome nepoznatom gradu...

724
01:09:55,958 --> 01:09:58,620
...ili verovati osobi...

725
01:10:00,429 --> 01:10:02,795
...koja zna mnogo o vama.

726
01:10:06,468 --> 01:10:08,231
Razmislite o tome.

727
01:11:00,456 --> 01:11:02,788
Ova haljina je pripadala mojoj zeni.

728
01:11:04,627 --> 01:11:05,958
Ali ja mislim...

729
01:11:06,962 --> 01:11:08,293
...da ce vam odgovarati.

730
01:11:08,964 --> 01:11:11,330
Ti...si ozenjen?

731
01:11:14,970 --> 01:11:15,959
Bio...

732
01:11:17,439 --> 01:11:19,134
... ja sam sada udovac..

733
01:11:19,308 --> 01:11:22,869
Oh..zao mi je...

734
01:11:23,178 --> 01:11:24,543
Nemoj vas biti zao.

735
01:11:24,647 --> 01:11:28,640
Nisam je voleo pa sam je ubio.

736
01:11:31,353 --> 01:11:32,411
Molim?

737
01:11:37,926 --> 01:11:39,689
Salim se.

738
01:11:41,897 --> 01:11:44,991
Ovo je soba za goste.

739
01:13:24,366 --> 01:13:25,492
Za tebe.

740
01:13:26,402 --> 01:13:29,030
Ja ne garantujem da cete se osecate
opusteno..

741
01:13:29,371 --> 01:13:31,805
..ali cete definitivno zaboraviti...

742
01:13:32,107 --> 01:13:34,075
... koliko ste umorni.

743
01:13:35,744 --> 01:13:37,041
Izvolite.

744
01:13:39,481 --> 01:13:40,743
Hvala.

745
01:13:40,849 --> 01:13:42,339
Sedite.

746
01:13:49,558 --> 01:13:51,992
Ako zelite napuniti telefon...

747
01:13:52,361 --> 01:13:55,057
...ili da obavestite nekoga gde ste...

748
01:13:55,397 --> 01:13:57,058
..onda slobodno to uradite.

749
01:13:58,667 --> 01:14:01,636
Posto vec znate toliko o meni..

750
01:14:01,804 --> 01:14:03,863
...sigurno ste pogodila da...

751
01:14:04,006 --> 01:14:07,498
...ne zelim da nikoga zovem.

752
01:14:10,579 --> 01:14:11,807
Dakle...

753
01:14:51,987 --> 01:15:00,326
''Uklonite stidljivost u vasim ocima,
stavite mrak pred vase oci.''

754
01:15:00,395 --> 01:15:08,302
''Ugasi zedj,
i ukloni vlagu sa mojih usana.''

755
01:15:08,403 --> 01:15:15,309
''Ja gorecu celu noc,
a ti me jutrom ugasi.''

756
01:15:23,986 --> 01:15:32,189
''Pusti da pokisnemo
u ovoj kisi danas.''

757
01:15:32,261 --> 01:15:42,501
''Pusti da pokisnem
u tvojoj kisi danas.''

758
01:15:49,845 --> 01:15:51,244
Prelepo.

759
01:15:52,180 --> 01:15:53,579
Ali...

760
01:15:55,050 --> 01:15:57,177
Ali su zatvoreni?

761
01:16:00,689 --> 01:16:01,747
Da.

762
01:16:03,492 --> 01:16:06,325
Zato sto ja volim divne stvari.

763
01:16:09,264 --> 01:16:14,258
''Hajde ispuni svoje zelje,
dodirni mi usne.''

764
01:16:14,336 --> 01:16:18,136
''I uradi ostatak zelja.''

765
01:16:18,473 --> 01:16:23,706
''Moje misli su razbacane.''

766
01:16:26,014 --> 01:16:30,713
''Hajde da spojimo nasa tela zajedno.''

767
01:16:31,019 --> 01:16:34,887
''Zapali srce ponovo.''

768
01:16:34,957 --> 01:16:40,896
''Dozvoli da probam tvoje usne.''

769
01:16:42,497 --> 01:16:50,336
''Ja gorecu celu noc,
ti me ujutru ugasi.''

770
01:16:50,739 --> 01:16:58,976
''Pusti da pokisnemo u
ovoj kisi danas.''

771
01:16:59,081 --> 01:17:09,218
''Pusti da pokisnem u
tvojoj kisi danas.''

772
01:17:18,533 --> 01:17:20,364
Udaj se za mene?

773
01:17:22,804 --> 01:17:25,170
Ali pre nego sto kazes da..
zelim da znas...

774
01:17:25,273 --> 01:17:27,935
...da su moji obicaji
drugaciji.

775
01:17:28,010 --> 01:17:32,811
''Dodji i ucini da ova noc bude duga.''

776
01:17:32,914 --> 01:17:36,873
''Upali iskru u srce moje.''

777
01:17:37,152 --> 01:17:43,091
''Ti si lisen sramote.''

778
01:17:44,493 --> 01:17:49,396
''Stavi tvoje usne na moje.''

779
01:17:49,498 --> 01:17:53,457
''Predji sve granice.''

780
01:17:53,769 --> 01:17:58,900
''Gde treba da se zaustavim,
molim te reci mi.''

781
01:18:01,076 --> 01:18:08,380
''Ja gorecu celu noc,
a ti me jutrom ohladi.''

782
01:18:09,351 --> 01:18:17,588
''Pusti da pokisnemo u ovoj
kisi danas.''

783
01:18:17,693 --> 01:18:28,399
''Pusti da pokisnem
u tvojoj kisi danas.''

784
01:21:45,433 --> 01:21:46,263
Da li si jos uvek budna.

785
01:21:48,103 --> 01:21:49,593
Skloni se od mene.

786
01:21:49,938 --> 01:21:52,406
Ti nisi Jaidev,
ti si neko drugi.

787
01:21:52,574 --> 01:21:54,769
Ja sam tvoj Jaidev.

788
01:21:55,143 --> 01:21:58,510
Jedina razlika je u tome
sto sada znas istinu...

789
01:21:58,580 --> 01:22:00,514
..koju nikada nisi smela saznati.

790
01:22:00,849 --> 01:22:02,441
Sta je istina?

791
01:22:02,517 --> 01:22:03,541
Sta si radio tamo?

792
01:22:03,652 --> 01:22:04,550
Molio se.

793
01:22:05,053 --> 01:22:08,284
Molio se,obozavao,
zrtvovao,..ali ne Bogu.

794
01:22:08,990 --> 01:22:10,389
Nego djavolu.

795
01:22:10,492 --> 01:22:11,720
Ne znam o cemu pricas?

796
01:22:11,826 --> 01:22:14,158
Znas tacno o cemu pricam.

797
01:22:14,429 --> 01:22:16,522
Izdao si me.

798
01:22:16,631 --> 01:22:18,292
Zasto si sakrio
to od mene?

799
01:22:18,366 --> 01:22:19,560
Jednostavno.

800
01:22:20,068 --> 01:22:21,831
Da si znala istinu o meni...

801
01:22:22,237 --> 01:22:24,034
..ti nebi ostala.

802
01:22:24,205 --> 01:22:25,866
Ti bi pobegla.

803
01:22:27,409 --> 01:22:30,708
Onda ne bih imao zamku za tebe
u mom srcu.

804
01:22:34,249 --> 01:22:35,978
Gde si krenula?

805
01:22:40,221 --> 01:22:44,157
Policija jos uvek traga
za vozacem koji je udario..

806
01:22:44,592 --> 01:22:47,527
...i ubio MLA sina.

807
01:22:50,465 --> 01:22:53,195
Nisi sposobna da prezivis
dan tamo.

808
01:22:53,535 --> 01:22:56,231
Jaidev,preklinjem te.

809
01:22:56,571 --> 01:23:00,701
Nikom necu reci tvoju tajnu.
Molim te pusti me da odem.

810
01:23:03,945 --> 01:23:07,540
Tama je mnogo jaca od
svetlosti.

811
01:23:07,649 --> 01:23:10,117
Ta snaga moze biti i tvoja.

812
01:23:10,185 --> 01:23:12,517
Ne zelim tu moc,pusti me.

813
01:23:14,022 --> 01:23:17,389
Bog vas cini slabim i plasljivim..

814
01:23:17,492 --> 01:23:19,460
...ali i dalje ga zovete dobronamernim.

815
01:23:21,696 --> 01:23:23,960
On je ucinio mnogu decu
gluvim,slepim i bolesnim od rodjenja..

816
01:23:24,032 --> 01:23:26,057
...jos kazete da je to simbol nade.

817
01:23:26,334 --> 01:23:27,301
Zar ne?

818
01:23:27,369 --> 01:23:28,563
Reci mi!

819
01:23:28,703 --> 01:23:31,035
On izaziva oluje,zemljotrese,
glad...

820
01:23:31,139 --> 01:23:33,130
...a vi ga zovete zastitnikom?

821
01:23:33,708 --> 01:23:36,404
Ako Bog postoji,
zasto ne ucini nesto?

822
01:23:36,544 --> 01:23:39,570
Zasto nestiti zene?
Ne nahrani gladne?

823
01:23:39,681 --> 01:23:41,512
Zato sto Bog ne postoji.

824
01:23:41,583 --> 01:23:45,212
Jedina stvar koja postoji su
djavo i njegova moc.

825
01:24:14,382 --> 01:24:15,815
Lekar u bolnici rekao je..

826
01:24:15,884 --> 01:24:18,910
...Jaidev nikada nece prohodati.

827
01:24:19,888 --> 01:24:22,186
On je paralizovan od struka na dole..

828
01:24:22,490 --> 01:24:24,515
..bice zavistan od nekoga svake sekunde..

829
01:24:24,592 --> 01:24:27,527
...on je sada zarobljen u svom telu.

830
01:24:27,962 --> 01:24:30,931
Mozda je to bio Boziji nacin
kaznjavanja...

831
01:24:31,032 --> 01:24:33,557
...ili ga je djavo obuzeo.

832
01:24:36,738 --> 01:24:41,198
Znao je da je imam priliku
da odem odavde.

833
01:24:41,676 --> 01:24:46,511
Imala sam poslednju stvar koju sam trebala
da uradim.

834
01:27:03,284 --> 01:27:05,980
Znam da zelis da pobegnes.

835
01:27:06,221 --> 01:27:11,022
Zelis da me ostavis
u svom zarobljenom telu.

836
01:27:11,559 --> 01:27:13,789
Ali to se nikada nece desiti.

837
01:27:14,229 --> 01:27:18,393
Pismo koje sada citas je kopija,
nije orginal..

838
01:27:19,000 --> 01:27:21,992
..orginal je kod mog advokata.

839
01:27:22,470 --> 01:27:25,871
..i u njemu se navodi da me zena mrzi...

840
01:27:25,940 --> 01:27:28,738
...i da je pokusala da me ubije..

841
01:27:29,244 --> 01:27:35,911
..I ako bude rekla da sam je ostavio,nestao
ili odjednom umro..

842
01:27:36,551 --> 01:27:41,181
..to je njen izgovor da sakrije istinu
o mojoj smrti..

843
01:27:41,422 --> 01:27:44,858
..takodje da znate da je devojka
veliki kriminalac...

844
01:27:45,260 --> 01:27:46,488
Ona je pobegla iz  Mumbaia...

845
01:27:46,561 --> 01:27:49,257
...nakon sto je ubila MLA
sina.

846
01:27:49,530 --> 01:27:54,900
Ako saznate da me je ostavila
onda znajte da sam mrtav.

847
01:27:55,069 --> 01:27:57,594
Ja sam uputio svoje advokate
o svemu..

848
01:27:57,739 --> 01:28:00,833
...ako nestanes ili umres...

849
01:28:01,209 --> 01:28:03,370
...ako odes.

850
01:28:04,045 --> 01:28:05,706
Sto se tice nas ako si zabrinuta...

851
01:28:05,880 --> 01:28:08,781
...moj duh je jak
da te zadrzi ovde.

852
01:28:09,117 --> 01:28:10,982
Ti ces ostati ovde zauvek.

853
01:28:11,052 --> 01:28:12,451
U ovome paklu.

854
01:28:12,654 --> 01:28:15,487
Ostacu ziv za tebe.

855
01:28:16,190 --> 01:28:20,388
A ako me pronadju mrtvog
ici ces u zatvor do kraja zivota.

856
01:28:20,728 --> 01:28:22,662
To ce biti zabavno?

857
01:28:23,965 --> 01:28:27,059
Citala sam ovo pismo svaki dan
zadnje dve godine.

858
01:28:42,383 --> 01:28:43,907
Pitam se...

859
01:28:44,152 --> 01:28:48,384
...kako neko moze da
pronadje pravu ljubav.

860
01:28:49,424 --> 01:28:51,324
Odlazi, Kabir.

861
01:28:51,492 --> 01:28:55,553
Jaidev me nikada nece pustiti da zivim
niti da odem.

862
01:28:56,664 --> 01:28:59,565
Ostacu ovde zauvek.

863
01:29:03,538 --> 01:29:04,835
Ne.

864
01:29:05,306 --> 01:29:07,035
Nisi ti jedina zarobljena.

865
01:29:07,709 --> 01:29:09,643
I ja sam, Meera.

866
01:29:10,845 --> 01:29:13,541
Ja sam bezao od zivota.

867
01:29:14,615 --> 01:29:19,484
Ja nikada nisam bio kompletan u vezi,
i u pricama.

868
01:29:20,555 --> 01:29:22,921
Ali necu odustati ovog puta.

869
01:29:23,891 --> 01:29:27,486
Uzecu te,makar izgubio svoj
zivot.

870
01:29:38,206 --> 01:29:39,138
Volim te.

871
01:29:39,874 --> 01:29:41,136
Volim i ja tebe.

872
01:29:43,378 --> 01:29:46,905
Ako je takva situacija,
onda imam resenje za to.

873
01:29:48,316 --> 01:29:51,183
Imacemo zadnji obred
za Jaidevo telo.

874
01:29:51,519 --> 01:29:53,248
A onda ce njegova dusa morati da napusti kucu.

875
01:29:53,354 --> 01:29:54,946
..zajedno sa njegovim telom.

876
01:29:56,190 --> 01:29:58,658
Ne,ako to uradimo,..

877
01:29:58,926 --> 01:30:01,759
...Jaidevov advokat
ce cuti o njegovom nestanku.

878
01:30:01,863 --> 01:30:04,991
Otvori ce pismo i
 Meera ce biti u zatvoru.

879
01:30:05,099 --> 01:30:07,693
Nema resenja za ovu situaciju.

880
01:30:11,139 --> 01:30:12,766
Ja imam ideju.

881
01:30:16,344 --> 01:30:18,209
Kabir, to nije resenje.

882
01:30:18,346 --> 01:30:20,177
Ako te uhvate mogu da te zatvore.

883
01:30:20,281 --> 01:30:21,714
Nema drugog nacina.

884
01:30:21,783 --> 01:30:23,717
Ima cemo razgovor sa ovim prvim
advokatom.

885
01:30:23,785 --> 01:30:25,377
Jedino nakon toga
se moze uciniti nesto sa Jaidevom.

886
01:30:25,453 --> 01:30:28,081
Ali..kako ces pronaci pismo?

887
01:30:28,189 --> 01:30:29,850
Uci cu u njegovu kancelariju.....

888
01:30:29,924 --> 01:30:31,516
...sacekacu da bude noc.

889
01:30:31,893 --> 01:30:33,053
Imas li adresu?

890
01:30:33,261 --> 01:30:34,193
Pise ovde.

891
01:30:34,362 --> 01:30:35,727
Shamit Noorie i sin.

892
01:30:35,797 --> 01:30:38,630
34/Hussain Street, Srinagar.

893
01:31:18,973 --> 01:31:21,567
- Shamit Noorie i sin,
je lazno ime.

894
01:31:21,742 --> 01:31:25,542
To je izveo sa slucajem koji
je onaj decko umrao u nesrecnom slucaju.

895
01:31:25,847 --> 01:31:27,371
Namit Shorey.

896
01:31:28,115 --> 01:31:29,946
Shamit Noorie.

897
01:31:30,351 --> 01:31:32,876
Cujem njegov govor u mojim usima.

898
01:31:33,120 --> 01:31:34,883
Zvuci kao da kaze...

899
01:31:35,423 --> 01:31:40,451
...''drzao sam te dve godine ovde
na osnovu lazi''.

900
01:31:41,562 --> 01:31:43,427
''Prevario sam te.''

901
01:31:43,531 --> 01:31:45,465
Do sada je Jaidev pobedjivao .

902
01:31:45,700 --> 01:31:47,964
Ali njegova igra ce se zavrsiti veceras.

903
01:31:48,369 --> 01:31:49,893
Stavicemo njegovo telo u krematorijumu...

904
01:31:49,971 --> 01:31:51,996
...i izvesti poslednji obred.

905
01:31:52,473 --> 01:31:53,940
Onda je sve gotovo.

906
01:31:54,108 --> 01:31:55,803
Da li moramo da ga odvedemo tamo?

907
01:31:56,010 --> 01:31:58,570
Mozemo ga spaliti ovde.
- Ne.

908
01:31:59,013 --> 01:32:01,038
Ne mozemo da ga spalimo.

909
01:32:01,148 --> 01:32:03,946
Moramo prvo uraditi poslednji ritual.

910
01:32:04,685 --> 01:32:07,017
A to moze da se uradi jedino u krematorijumu.

911
01:32:07,121 --> 01:32:09,919
Ako ga jednostavno spalimo
njegov duh ce i dalje proganjati.

912
01:32:10,658 --> 01:32:12,421
A njegovo telo ce ostati netaknuto..

913
01:32:12,527 --> 01:32:14,324
...dok ne stignemo do krematorijuma.

914
01:32:50,865 --> 01:32:51,957
Motor je pregrejan.

915
01:32:52,767 --> 01:32:53,734
Treba nam voda.

916
01:32:53,801 --> 01:32:54,859
Ali kako cemo sada.

917
01:32:54,936 --> 01:32:56,597
Meera ako ne sipam vodu 
motor nece raditi.

918
01:32:56,704 --> 01:32:58,604
Ne mozemo njegovo telo nositi pesice.

919
01:33:02,743 --> 01:33:04,472
Primetio sam vodopad na putu.

920
01:33:05,746 --> 01:33:06,838
Uradicu nesto.

921
01:33:07,481 --> 01:33:08,470
Strah me je.

922
01:33:08,549 --> 01:33:10,016
Ostani u autu.

923
01:33:10,718 --> 01:33:12,913
I ne izlazi po svaku cenu.

924
01:33:13,254 --> 01:33:14,687
Odmah se vracam.

925
01:33:49,690 --> 01:33:51,988
Meera!

926
01:34:00,835 --> 01:34:01,802
Kabir.

927
01:35:31,926 --> 01:35:33,894
Meera! Meera! Meera!

928
01:35:35,296 --> 01:35:36,422
Meera! Sta se dogodilo?

929
01:35:36,530 --> 01:35:37,690
Sta radis ovde?

930
01:35:37,765 --> 01:35:38,732
Ja...

931
01:35:39,934 --> 01:35:41,026
JA...

932
01:35:41,368 --> 01:35:42,960
ja..
-Nije to nista.

933
01:35:43,871 --> 01:35:45,395
